{"tid":1689984,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（十萬火急）有咩同遊行一樣咁重要？！？！","createTime":"2019-11-03T05:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T17:18:46.000Z","uid":333204,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5948cc9f7690f3d7a09edcae40fc2409080a8370","tid":1689984,"uid":333204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:56:56.000Z","msg":"各位手足：<br />\n<br />\n除咗遊行，仲有一樣好重要啊！<br />\n<br />\n亦係大家都一定可以做到！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就係1124區議會投票日！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n投票攻略已經有人講過就唔再多講。但有兩點想提提大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 事關已經有大量手足被捕/被跳樓/被拘留，即係話呢班人好難有機會或已經無機會去到投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即係我方嘅票數又少左。所以選舉前一星期<span style=\"color: red;\">不建議</span>開花/勇武/裝修。轉啲和理非嘅活動，直頭唔好俾理狗有機會拉人。我明大家好怕停低之後追唔返/俾狗有時間秋後算賬，但諗真啲好多手足都好後生，後生到連選民資格都未有⋯所以有票喺手嘅，真係要盡量減低被捕機會，以免因為無得保釋各種原因而無得去投票！<br />\n<br />\n2. 吹雞！<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">海外</span></span>班香港人同我用盡你嘅方法返香港投票！！<br />\n我知道好難，要買機票要放低嗰邊嘅工作同生活，但香港要人！你嗰一票絕對能夠影響到香港嘅未來！！你唔係咁衰仔掉低香港人啊嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 1124邊個去因為旅行無去投票嘅，屌你港豬都哂氣，自己去天堂同班手足/義士交代！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，麻煩文宣手足做嘢，要文宣叫班有選民資格嘅香港人返嚟投票啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫推啊！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">票投民賤聯 香港玩撚完</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6srwcci.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6srwcci.jpg&h=8e664a09&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kELpxcj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkELpxcj.jpg&h=3ce94e58&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zZjtYSk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzZjtYSk.jpg&h=51f24595&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"adb6ad6eb19598d7866d9dcb63fcd5b99bfe809d","tid":1689984,"uid":333204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:57:30.000Z","msg":"幫推啊"},{"pid":"aadb8b4d8e6991d2f78c559d682ccf1abaa1a7ee","tid":1689984,"uid":333204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:58:00.000Z","msg":"扮推 推到有人睇到"},{"pid":"f44754aafdc6171224e8b22688718948d1fe2b9b","tid":1689984,"uid":114101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:01:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9100dac73af1ef1fb0d641d7c247fd2dcba84031","tid":1689984,"uid":333204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:05:19.000Z","msg":"重要啊 唔好沉啊"},{"pid":"54c38d2d828220c8d375292254fba32286999cf7","tid":1689984,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:09:29.000Z","msg":"中後排可唔可以click入黎睇睇 thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出到黎可唔可以緊張少少 審時度勢..<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689923</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"481aed7ecc00c5b0836ef0a2d3c37436de0c62d8","tid":1689984,"uid":333204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f44754aafdc6171224e8b22688718948d1fe2b9b","tid":1689984,"uid":114101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:01:57.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:10:03.000Z","msg":"推多幾下啦 好人一世平安"},{"pid":"1ae8002d55aa362cdd1b77f5ddaea909384dd896","tid":1689984,"uid":119585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:13:28.000Z","msg":"【行動post】早上抗爭 堅諗得過<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689916\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689916</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"db6daf1d5290c6e38052bb811397a07e5174d4aa","t